<p>Seeing a blind dead man in a dream means following forbidden things and other interpretations, and we will explain that to the unmarried woman, the married woman, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > the pregnant woman </a>, the divorced woman, and the man, as I saw a dead man who became blind, or that my deceased brother was blind, or my dead father was blind at <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a>, and more on the subject:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the death of the blind in a dream</span></h2>
<p>If you saw a dead man blind in a dream, and he saw him in this world, then this indicates his great oppression of himself, to the point that he made himself fall into the evil of his deeds.<br/>It has been said that seeing the deceased blind in a dream is considered an unfavorable vision and indicates that the person is not living a righteous life, and the vision may indicate the collection of money through forbidden means.<br/>Whoever sees that a dead person has become blind in a dream, this means that he is not on the right path in his life.</p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-شخص-في-المنام?page=1714" > Seeing a person </a> you know that he has become blind in a dream means that unfortunate events will soon happen to the dreamer, and this vision may indicate that he is following an unworthy person or that he may face problems because of bad friends.<br/>The blind dead man in the dream indicates that you are entering into illegitimate projects that may be commercial projects that harm others or cut off their livelihood.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
