<p><span></span></p>
<p>Whoever sees that the dead person has become blind and cannot see in a dream, this is a sign that the dreamer has fallen into mistakes and undesirable actions that will damage his reputation among people. This vision is considered a warning to him that he should repent and abandon sins and forbidden things.</p>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الرجل-في-المنام?page=447" > man </a> <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الأعمى-الميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=394" > blind dead </a> in a dream may be an indication that the dreamer will go through problems and troubles, and that his circumstances will not be good, especially financially.<br/>Whoever sees someone he knows who has died and is blind in a dream, this indicates that the place where he lives is full of fraud and deception, and he is not affected by it, and he should remain righteous.</p>
<p>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الموتى-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=956" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الموت-في-المنام?page=3945" > the dead </a> </a> who are blind in a dream means that you are following deception, living in doubt, and far from guidance and justice.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
