<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=813" > dead person </a> blind may indicate that this dead person needs begging and asking for forgiveness and paying alms to him.</p>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-شخص-في-المنام?page=1714" > person </a> blind dead in a dream means that the dreamer will commit fornication with a woman or steal people's money, and the dream is a warning to the dreamer that he should not follow the desires and actions of the devil.</p>
<p>And the dream of a man <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الأعمى-الميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=394" > blind dead </a> who regained his sight, this vision shows the end of injustice and shows the victory of right over wrong.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
