<p><span></span></p>
<p>If the dreamer sees that he is healing a blind person and making him see again, this means that the dreamer will be able to achieve his goals and satisfy his desires and get rid of worries and sorrows.</p>
<p>As for the vision that the deceased now sees well in the dream, this vision is praiseworthy and indicates that the dreamer will declare repentance and return to the right path and stay away from forbidden actions and unlawful means of livelihood.  .</p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الميت-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=813" > Seeing the dead </a> in a dream means that the dreamer will be a good person and will enjoy <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الحب-والاحترام?page=2119" > love and respect </a> from the people around him, and because of his good deeds he will have a good reputation.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
