<h2><span>Interpretation of the death of the blind father in a dream</span></h2>
<p>If you saw your deceased father blind in a dream, this means that the dreamer is living on unlawful money that is earned through illegal means.</p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الأب-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3719" > Seeing the father </a> dead blind in a dream is a sign of committing sins and disobedience and abandoning the path of truth.<br/>Whoever sees that his deceased father is blind in the vision, this indicates that changes will occur in the dreamer's life, but these changes will be for the worse and are not positive changes at all.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the death of a blind mother in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Whoever sees that the dead mother has become blind in a dream, this vision is not worthy of praise and indicates the emergence of differences between the dreamer and other family members.<br/>If the dreamer sees that his deceased mother is no longer seen in a dream, this means that the dreamer will face difficult days and will live with financial problems and find it difficult to meet his needs.<br/>If an <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-غير-المتزوجة-لابن-سيرين?page=786" > unmarried woman </a> sees her deceased mother blind in a dream, this indicates the emergence of emotional problems and may indicate the existence of a relationship with an unsuitable person.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
