</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the death of the blind brother in a dream</span></h2>
<p>And the dream interpreter, <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a>, mentions that <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الأخ-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=544" > seeing the brother </a> dead blind in a dream, and that the vision indicates the occurrence of bad events, and the vision may indicate that the dreamer is exposed to illness or suffering from anxiety.<br/>Seeing a dead brother who does not see him in a dream means that you are entering into unprofitable businesses and institutions, which will lead to <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-خسارة-المال?page=3819" > loss of money </a>.<br/>If an <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-غير-المتزوجة-لابن-سيرين?page=786" > unmarried woman </a> sees that the deceased brother is blind in a dream, this means that she will enter into a failed relationship or may delay marriage.<br/>If a married woman sees that her dead brother has become blind in her dream, this indicates her involvement in problems with people, and these problems will cause a lot of marital strife.</p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > A pregnant woman </a> who sees that her brother has died blind, and this vision indicates that she suffers from health problems during <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الحمل-والولادة-لابن-سيرين?page=1" > pregnancy and childbirth </a>.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the death of the blind sister in a dream</span></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الأخ-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=544" > Seeing the sister </a> dead blind in a dream means that the dreamer is neglecting his religious duties such as fasting, prayer, and others.<br/>If he sees that the dead sister has become invisible in a dream, this indicates the abundance of sins and sins that the dreamer has committed.<br/>And if you see the dead sister sick or bleeding, this indicates that you are entering into an illegitimate trade and taking money from the forbidden.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
