<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-موت-الزوج-في-المنام?page=2147" > the death of the husband </a> blind in a dream</span></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> says that if the dead husband appears blind in a dream, then this vision indicates that the husband in his life did not do good deeds and did not perform worship as required.<br/>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-زوج-ميت-في-المنام?page=4023" > dead husband </a> blind in a dream means that he needs begging and giving alms and distributing rewards and asking God to forgive him.<br/>If the deceased husband is seen suffering from an eye disease, this indicates that he has debts that he did not pay off in his life and asks the one who saw her to pay them off.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-موت-طفل-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=357" > the death of a child </a> blind in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-طفل-ميت-في-المنام?page=2547" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-طفل-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=868" > child </a> dead </a> blind in a dream indicates that there are many problems in the dreamer's life, and the vision may indicate the commission of sins and transgressions, so the person must return to God and seek forgiveness.<br/>A <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant woman </a> who sees a dead child blind while she is asleep indicates the difficulty of childbirth and indicates that she will face health problems during childbirth.<br/>Whoever sees that the child has regained his sight in a dream, this indicates the end of sorrows, a change in circumstances, and an increase in livelihood.</p>
